title: High-speed t-shirt bag making machine US-CW-400V2
title_uz: Maykali paket ishlab chiqarish uskunasi US-CW-400V2
title_en: High-speed t-shirt bag making machine US-CW-400V2
short_description: Equipment for the production of T-shirt bags also varies. One of them is this US-CW-400V2 device. This equipment has 2 lines, each line produces up to 250 bags per minute, and the product width is up to 400 mm, and the length is from 370 mm to 700 mm. This equipment with a total power of 18.5 kW weighs 3100 kg. Dimensions: length 8000 mm, width 1850 mm and height 1800 mm. The recommendation also includes other models of this equipment. Their prices and parameters differ from each other.
short_description_uz: Maykali paket ishlab chiqarish uskunalari ham turlicha bo'ladi. Ulardan biri shu US-CW-400V2 uskunadir. Bu uskuna 2 qatorli bo'lib, har bir qatorda daqiqasiga 250 tagacha paket ishlab chiqariladi va mahsulotning kengligi 400 mm gacha, uzunligi esa 370 mm dan 700 mm gacha yetadi. Umumiy quvvati 18.5 kW ni tashkil etuvchi bu uskuna 3100 kg vaznga ega. O'lchamlari: uzunligi 8000 mm, kengligi 1850 mm va balandligi 1800 mm. Tavsida bu uskunaning boshqa modellari ham aks etgan. Ularning narx va parametrlari bir-biridan farq qiladi.
